  <p><b><span id="Overview">Objective:</span></b> <span id="md-webpage-description" itemprop="description"><i>ITIL Demand Management</i> aims to understand, anticipate and influence customer demand for services. This process works with Capacity Management to ensure that the service provider has sufficient capacity to meet the required demand for particular services.</span></p>
